      "name": "Engolir",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A criatura swallows a Small ou menor target it is grappling. Enquanto swallowed, o alvo isn't Agarrado but has the Cego e Impedido conditions, e ela tem Total Cover against attacks e other effects outside a criatura. Enquanto swallowing o alvo, a criatura can't use Mordida, e se a criatura dies, the swallowed target is no longer Impedido e can escape de the corpse using 1,5 m de movimento, exiting com a condição Caído.\nAt the end de da criatura next turn, the swallowed target takes 5 (2d4) dano de ácido. Se that de dano doesn't kill it, a criatura disgorges it, causing it to exit Caído.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
